*. Reprinted in volume 1 of his collected works, p. 65–75, . On page 120 Gel&#x27;fand suggests that the index of an elliptic operator should be expressible in terms of topological data.
*
*. This describes the original proof of the index theorem. (Atiyah and Singer never published their original proof themselves, but only improved versions of it.)
